    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.8.1/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-50oBUHEmvpQ+1lW4y57PTFmhCaXp0ML5d60M1M7uH2+nqUivzIebhndOJK28anvf" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat&family=Crete+Round&family=Delius&family=Eczar&family=Josefin+Slab:wght@300&family=Mochiy+Pop+One&family=Nunito&family=Pacifico&family=Ubuntu&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column vh-100" style="background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1566437036079-0e00cc9ea796?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=435&q=80);background-repeat: no-repeat;background-size: cover;background-position: center;">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-light bg-info sticky-top">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" style="margin-left: 8px;"><i class="fa fa-globe" style="font-size: 26px;"></i> GlobeStatus</a>
          <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-controls="navbarNavAltMarkup" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
          </button>
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavAltMarkup">
            <div class="navbar-nav">
                <a class="nav-link mx-1" href="/GlobeStatus/currentWeatherByName">By Name</a>
                <a class="nav-link " href="/GlobeStatus/currentWeatherByCoordinates">By Coordinates</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <div class="container mt-5 mb-4">
          <div class="row mb-2" style="color: white;">
              <div class="col-md-6 px-5">
                  <h1 class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-globe" style="font-size: 33px;"></i> GlobeStatus</h1>
                  <p class="text-center mb-1 mt-3">
                      Welcome to GlobeStatus, here we provide you current weather condition Data of any city throughout the globe.
                      You can search any city by its name via geocoding or by the city's coordinates. We use mapbox for displaying cities on map which you searched to make your experience worth a while.
                  </p>
                  <a class="btn btn-info px-4 mt-4" style="display:block" href="/GlobeStatus/currentWeatherByName">Search By City Name</a>
                  <a class="btn btn-info px-4 mt-1" style="display:block" href="/GlobeStatus/currentWeatherByCoordinates">Search By City Coordinates</a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div id='map'  style='width: 100%; height: 290px;border-radius: 10px;' class="mb-2"></div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row mt-5 mb-3" style="color: white;">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img-fluid" style="width: 100%; height: 290px;border-radius: 7px;" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611273426858-450d8e3c9fce?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 py-5 px-5">
                <h1 class="text-center">
                    <h1 class="text-center"><i class="fas fa-fire"></i> Air Pollution</h1>
                <p class="text-center mb-1 mt-3">
                    Air pollution is a global issue which we cannot simply neglect, that is why for every city you search we provide a detailed air pollution data for that city such as the air quality index (AQI), composition of harmful components and much more.
                </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row mt-5" style="color:white">
              <div class="col-md-6 px-5 py-5" >
                <h1 class="text-center"><svg class="bi flex-shrink-0 me-2" width="35" height="42" style="color: white;" role="img" aria-label="Danger:"><use xlink:href="#exclamation-triangle-fill"/></svg> Weather Forecast</h1>
                <p class="text-center mb-1 mt-3">
                    We provide 5 days weather forecast for any location on the globe. Each days's forecast comes with a three hour step size.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <img class="img-fluid" style="width: 100%; height: 290px;border-radius: 7px;" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558448495-5ef3fce92344?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1170&q=80">
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    

      <footer class="footer py-2 mt-auto bg-info">
        <div class="container">
            <span class="text-dark">&copy; GlobeStatus 2022</span>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <script> 
    maptilersdk.config.apiKey = `2cBE8DScQJsBf7upDtt0`;
    const map = new maptilersdk.Map({
    container: 'map',
    style: maptilersdk.MapStyle.BRIGHT,
    center: [<%=delhiCoordinates.longitude%>, <%=delhiCoordinates.latitude%>],
    zoom: 10 
    });

    new maptilersdk.Marker()
    .setLngLat([<%=delhiCoordinates.longitude%>, <%=delhiCoordinates.latitude%>])
    .setPopup(
        new maptilersdk.Popup({ offset: 25 })
    )
    .addTo(map)
    </script>
</body>
</html>